				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Baelen sits in the Myconid Circle, talking to himself. He narrowly escaped being blown up by a field of mushrooms with the help of the player. He may react to his wife Derryth being dead, and may also have his wits returned to him after eating the noblestalk mushroom.\r\nThese comments loop."
